OverWorld
1. Sprites - Chrono Trigger Sprites
2. Top Down Game

Combat
1. Overworld Chrono Trigger Style with Player Interactive Combat.


Weapons Specifications
1. Must be Uniqe in the Timing Window
2. Short Sword - Fast slash timing
3. Great Sword - Like circus bell swing - maybe mash to fill bar then press attack again on contact for more damage.
4. Knife - metronome - multiple hits if you get the timing right.
5. Sniper - Like aiming a koopa in paper mario
6. Buzz Saw - Approach the user, mash specific inputs like ps2 naruto


Difficutly - how to make it hard
1. Timing windows are faster then paper mario
2. Make it little room for error
